('algoryx-algodoo', 'Algodoo', 'Algodoo is a unique 2D-simulation software from Algoryx Simulation AB. Algodoo is designed in a playful, cartoony manner, making it a perfect tool for creating interactive scenes. Explore physics, build amazing inventions, design cool games or experiment with Algodoo in your science classes. Algodoo encourages students and children’s own creativity, ability and motivation to construct knowledge while having fun. Making it as entertaining as it is educational. Algodoo is also a perfect aid for children to learn and practice physics at home.', 'Games', 'algoryx-algodoo-icon', ''),
('alibaba-alibabacloudcli', 'Alibaba Cloud CLI', 'Alibaba Cloud Command Line Interface (Alibaba Cloud CLI) is an open source tool built on the Alibaba Cloud SDK for Go. You can use the aliyun command to interact with other Alibaba Cloud services to manage your Alibaba Cloud resources.
Alibaba Cloud CLI can directly access the Alibaba cloud product OpenAPI. You can manage and maintain your own Alibaba Cloud resources by developing the shell script based on Alibaba Cloud CLI. Make sure that you have activated the cloud product you want to use and understand the API usage of the product.', 'Development', 'alibaba-alibabacloudcli-icon', ''),
('alibaba-dingtalk', 'DingTalk', 'DingTalk is an intelligent working platform created by Alibaba Group to support tens of millions of enterprises to achieve higher working efficiency with the new digitalized working method.', 'Development', 'alibaba-dingtalk-icon', ''),
('alibaba-dingtalk-lite', 'DingTalk Lite', 'DingTalk is an intelligent working platform created by Alibaba Group to support tens of millions of enterprises to achieve higher working efficiency with the new digitalized working method.', 'Development', 'alibaba-dingtalk-lite-icon', ''),
('alibaba-lightproxy', 'LightProxy', 'LightProxy is an open-source web debugging proxy alternative to Charles, which is based on whistle & Electron.', 'Utilities', 'alibaba-lightproxy-icon', ''),
('alibaba-teambition', 'Teambition', 'Teambition is a team collaboration tool by Alibaba that promotes collaboration in enterprise and team through visual management of projects and tasks, making it simple, relaxing and enjoyable. It is suitable for various types of teams such as product, R&D, design, marketing, operation, sales, HR, etc.', 'Design', 'alibaba-teambition-icon', ''),
('alist-alist', 'Alist', 'A file list program that supports multiple storage, powered by Gin and Solidjs.', 'Utilities', 'alist-alist-icon', ''),
('allmapsoft-microsoftvirtualearthsatellite', 'Microsoft Virtualearth Satellite Downloader', 'This is a tool that can automatically download the Bing satellite maps images to your PC. It can download the small tiles and save them to your hard disk. After downloading, you can view the maps offline by its tool Maps Viewer.', 'Design', 'allmapsoft-microsoftvirtualearthsatellite-icon', ''),
('allen&heath-ahmsystemmanager', 'AHM System Manager', 'AHM System Manager software and AHM-64’s flexible architecture allow rapid configuration, with no certified programming training required.', 'Development', 'allen&heath-ahmsystemmanager-icon', ''),
('allen&heath-avantisdirector', 'Avantis Director', 'Avantis Director is a free Windows and Mac OS application enabling offline editing and online control capabilities. Offline mode can be used for the creation and editing of show files and system configuration, as well as serving as a training tool for new users. Online mode delivers full remote-control of the mixer, freeing the engineer from the mix position to make changes from anywhere in the venue.', 'Audio', 'allen&heath-avantisdirector-icon', ''),
('allen&heath-customcontroleditor', 'Custom Control Editor', 'Custom Control Editor 1.1.1 Setup', 'Design', 'allen&heath-customcontroleditor-icon', ''),
('allen&heath-sqmixpad', 'SQ MixPad', 'SQ MixPad 1.5.0 Setup', 'Utilities', 'allen&heath-sqmixpad-icon', ''),
('allen&heath-dlivedirector', 'dLive Director', 'A multi-platform editor and control software for dLive. It lets you configure the system offline before the show, check and edit Show files from guest engineers, and control the mix live using a laptop or touch tablet. dLive Director has a touch-friendly interface, with resizable fader banks to suit different resolutions from pro tablets to large touch screens / all-in-ones. A Touchscreen view replicates every aspect of the dLive Surface GUI for instant familiarity to all dLive users.', 'Audio', 'allen&heath-dlivedirector-icon', ''),
('allroundautomations-plsqldeveloper', 'PL/SQL Developer', 'PL/SQL Developer is an Integrated Development Environment for developing, testing, debugging and optimizing Oracle PL/SQL stored program units like packages, triggers and so on. PL/SQL Developer features context sensitive help and database object descriptions, syntax highlighting, data querying and editing, a graphical browser, and other functions to make a developer’s life easier.', 'Development', 'allroundautomations-plsqldeveloper-icon', ''),
('almico-speedfan', 'SpeedFan', 'SpeedFan is a program that monitors voltages, fan speeds and temperatures in computers with hardware monitor chips.', 'Utilities', 'almico-speedfan-icon', ''),
('alphayama-poweriast', 'PowerIAST', 'Easily create diacritic letters to transliterate Sanskrit (and other Indian languages). Based on the PowerAccent project.', 'Utilities', 'alphayama-poweriast-icon', ''),
('altdrag-altdrag', 'AltDrag', 'Easily drag windows when pressing the alt key', 'Utilities', 'altdrag-altdrag-icon', ''),
('altsnap-altsnap', 'AltSnap', 'Easily drag windows when pressing the alt key. Unofficial fork of AltDrag from Stefan Sundin', 'Utilities', 'altsnap-altsnap-icon', ''),
('altap-salamander', 'Altap Salamander', 'Altap Salamander is a fast and reliable two-panel file manager for Windows. It has an intuitive interface, offers viewers for all popular file formats as well as support for common archives, and has built-in FTP and SFTP clients.', 'Utilities', 'altap-salamander-icon', ''),
('amanharwara-altus', 'Altus', 'Desktop client for WhatsApp Web with themes & multiple account support.', 'Utilities', 'amanharwara-altus-icon', ''),
('amazon-awscli', 'AWS Command Line Interface', 'The AWS CLI is an open source tool built on top of the AWS SDK for Python (Boto) that provides commands for interacting with AWS services. With minimal configuration, you can start using all of the functionality provided by the AWS Management Console from your favorite terminal program.', 'Development', 'amazon-awscli-icon', ''),
('amazon-awsvpnclient', 'AWS VPN Client', 'Securely access AWS resources and resources in your on-premises network.', 'Utilities', 'amazon-awsvpnclient-icon', ''),
('amazon-chime', 'Amazon Chime', 'Amazon Chime is a communications service that lets you meet, chat, and place business calls inside and outside your organization, all using a single application.', 'Development', 'amazon-chime-icon', ''),
('amazon-corretto-11', 'Amazon Corretto 11', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-11-icon', ''),
('amazon-corretto-17', 'Amazon Corretto 17', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-17-icon', ''),
('amazon-corretto-18', 'Amazon Corretto 18', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-18-icon', ''),
('amazon-corretto-19', 'Amazon Corretto 19', 'Amazon Corretto is a no-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK). Corretto comes with long-term support that will include performance enhancements and security fixes. Amazon runs Corretto internally on thousands of production services and Corretto is certified as compatible with the Java SE standard. With Corretto, you can develop and run Java applications on popular operating systems, including Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-19-icon', ''),
('amazon-corretto-8', 'Amazon Corretto 8', 'No-cost, multiplatform, production-ready distribution of the Open Java Development Kit (OpenJDK).', 'Development', 'amazon-corretto-8-icon', ''),
('amazon-games', 'Amazon Games', 'Amazon Games app is a Windows PC game launcher that allows you to claim, download, and play new and classic Windows PC games every month from Prime Gaming.', 'Games', 'amazon-games-icon', ''),
('amazon-kindle', 'Amazon Kindle', 'The Kindle app is available for most major smartphones, tablets and computers. That means with our free Kindle reading apps, you can buy a Kindle book once, and read it on any device with the Kindle app installed*. You can also read that same Kindle book on a Kindle device if you own one.', 'Design', 'amazon-kindle-icon', '');

INSERT INTO apps (id, name, description, category, icon, linux_alternative) VALUES
('amazon-music', 'Amazon Music', 'Amazon.Music', 'Audio', 'amazon-music-icon', ''),
('amazon-nosqlworkbench', 'NoSQL Workbench', 'NoSQL Workbench is a unified visual IDE tool that provides data modeling, data visualization, and query development features to help you design, create, query, and manage DynamoDB tables.', 'Development', 'amazon-nosqlworkbench-icon', ''),
('amazon-opensearch-odbc', 'OpenSearch SQL ODBC Driver', 'OpenSearchODBC is a read-only ODBC driver for Windows and Mac for connecting to OpenSearch SQL support.', 'Development', 'amazon-opensearch-odbc-icon', ''),
('amazon-sam-cli', 'AWS SAM Command Line Interface', 'The AWS Serverless Application Model (SAM) is an open-source framework for building serverless applications.', 'Utilities', 'amazon-sam-cli-icon', ''),
('amazon-sendtokindle', 'Amazon Send to Kindle', 'Send to Kindle will appear when you right click on a file in Windows Explorer or in the print dialog of any Windows application. To send multiple documents to Kindle without opening them, simply select documents and choose Send to Kindle from the right-click menu in Windows Explorer. You can download archived personal documents from any Kindle device or using the free reading app on your iOS or Android device. Whispersync of notes, highlights, bookmarks and last page read is available on your archived personal documents that have been converted into Kindle format.', 'Office', 'amazon-sendtokindle-icon', ''),
('amazon-sessionmanagerplugin', 'Session Manager Plugin', 'This plugin helps you to use the AWS Command Line Interface (AWS CLI) to start and end sessions to your managed instances.', 'Design', 'amazon-sessionmanagerplugin-icon', ''),
('amazon-workspacesclient', 'Amazon WorkSpaces', 'Amazon WorkSpaces offers an easy way to provide a cloud-based desktop experience to your end users.', 'Development', 'amazon-workspacesclient-icon', ''),
('aminemouafik-ferdi', 'Ferdi', 'Ferdi is a desktop app that helps you organize how you use your favourite apps by combining them into one application. It is based on Franz - a software already used by thousands of people - with the difference that Ferdi gives you many additional features and doesn''t restrict its usage! Ferdi is compatible with your existing Franz account so you can continue right where you left off. Find out more about Ferdi and its features on getferdi.com.', 'Social', 'aminemouafik-ferdi-icon', ''),
('anaconda-anaconda3', 'Anaconda3', 'Anaconda Individual Edition is the easiest way to perform Python/R data science and machine learning on a single machine. Developed for solo practitioners, it is the toolkit that equips you to work with thousands of open-source packages and libraries.', 'Development', 'anaconda-anaconda3-icon', ''),
('anaconda-miniconda3', 'Miniconda3', 'Miniconda is a free minimal installer for conda. It is a small, bootstrap version of Anaconda that includes only conda, Python, the packages they depend on, and a small number of other useful packages, including pip, zlib and a few others.', 'Utilities', 'anaconda-miniconda3-icon', ''),
('anchorfree-touchvpn', 'TouchVPN', 'A free VPN', 'Utilities', 'anchorfree-touchvpn-icon', ''),
('andersama-obs-asio', 'obs-asio', 'ASIO plugin for OBS-Studio', 'Utilities', 'andersama-obs-asio-icon', ''),
('andrewiethoff-exactaudiocopy', 'Exact Audio Copy', 'Exact Audio Copy is a so-called audio grabber for audio CDs using standard CD and DVD-ROM drives.', 'Audio', 'andrewiethoff-exactaudiocopy-icon', ''),
('andreaswascher-repoz', 'RepoZ', 'RepoZ is a zero-conf git repository hub with Windows Explorer & CLI-enhancements.', 'Development', 'andreaswascher-repoz-icon', ''),
('andresmorelos-invoncify', 'Invoncify', 'Flexible invoicing desktop app with beautiful & customizable templates', 'Social', 'andresmorelos-invoncify-icon', ''),
('andrewzhezherun-windjview', 'WinDjView', 'WinDjView is a fast, compact and powerful DjVu viewer for Windows with tabbed interface, continuous scrolling and advanced printing options.', 'Utilities', 'andrewzhezherun-windjview-icon', ''),
('angusjohnson-pdftkbuilder', 'PDFTK Builder', 'Take control of your PDF documents - merge or split pages; stamp pages or add background watermarks; add page numbers; and even rotate pages.', 'Office', 'angusjohnson-pdftkbuilder-icon', ''),
('angusjohnson-resourcehacker', 'Resource Hacker', 'Resource Hacker is a program that allows you to compile and decompile various resources and file types.', 'Development', 'angusjohnson-resourcehacker-icon', ''),
('anjok07-ultimatevocalremover', 'Ultimate Vocal Remover', 'This application uses state-of-the-art source separation models to remove vocals from audio files. UVR''s core developers trained all of the models provided in this package (except for the Demucs v3 4-stem models).', 'Development', 'anjok07-ultimatevocalremover-icon', ''),
('anki-anki', 'Anki', 'Anki is a program which makes remembering things easy.
Because it''s a lot more efficient than traditional study methods, you can either greatly decrease your time spent studying, or greatly increase the amount you learn.
Anyone who needs to remember things in their daily life can benefit from Anki.
Since it is content-agnostic and supports images, audio, videos and scientific markup (via LaTeX), the possibilities are endless.', 'Development', 'anki-anki-icon', ''),
('antsoftware-antrenamer', 'Ant Renamer', 'Ant Renamer is a free program that makes easier the renaming of lots of files and folders by using specified settings. It supports Unicode names.', 'Development', 'antsoftware-antrenamer-icon', ''),
('anthonybeaumont-achievementwatcher', 'Achievement Watcher', 'Achievement Watcher allows you to view every achievement earned on your PC whether it''s coming from Steam, a Steam emulator, and more.', 'Games', 'anthonybeaumont-achievementwatcher-icon', ''),
('antimicro-antimicro', 'AntiMicro', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support', 'Games', 'antimicro-antimicro-icon', ''),
('antimicrox-antimicrox', 'AntiMicroX', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support.', 'Games', 'antimicrox-antimicrox-icon', ''),
('antimicrox-antimicroxportable', 'AntiMicroX Portable', 'Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad. Useful for playing games with no gamepad support.', 'Games', 'antimicrox-antimicroxportable-icon', ''),
('antibodysoftware-bulkimagedownloader', 'Bulk Image Downloader', 'Bulk Image Downloader (BID) is a simple to use yet powerful image downloading tool for Windows PCs.', 'Design', 'antibodysoftware-bulkimagedownloader-icon', ''),
('antibodysoftware-wizfile', 'WizFile', 'Find files by name on your hard drives almost instantly.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wizfile-icon', ''),
('antibodysoftware-wizkey', 'WizKey', 'WizKey is a keyboard enhancement utility that makes the typing of accented and other special characters easy. The most common characters can be typed using easy to remember keyboard shortcuts, and less common characters can be selected and searched for by code or name using the built in Unicode character browser.', 'Development', 'antibodysoftware-wizkey-icon', ''),
('antibodysoftware-wizmouse', 'WizMouse', 'WizMouse is a mouse enhancement utility that makes your mouse wheel work on the window currently under the mouse pointer, instead of the currently focused window. This means you no longer have to click on a window before being able to scroll it with the mouse wheel.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wizmouse-icon', ''),
('antibodysoftware-wiztree', 'WizTree', 'WizTree is a hard drive disk space analyser similar to WinDirStat but is MUCH faster.', 'Utilities', 'antibodysoftware-wiztree-icon', ''),
('antoineaflalo-soundswitch', 'SoundSwitch', 'No more navigating through several menus and screens. Just configure SoundSwitch once - and you are able to switch between your devices as fast as never before!', 'Audio', 'antoineaflalo-soundswitch-icon', ''),
('antonikepinski-parsifydesktop', 'Parsify Desktop', 'Extendable calculator for the 21st Century ⚡', 'Utilities', 'antonikepinski-parsifydesktop-icon', ''),
('antonycourtney-tad', 'Tad', 'Tabular data viewer desktop app, built with Electron', 'Utilities', 'antonycourtney-tad-icon', ''),
('antutu-antutubenchmark', 'Antutu Benchmark', 'A trusted computer performance measurement expert', 'Utilities', 'antutu-antutubenchmark-icon', ''),
('anydesksoftwaregmbh-anydesk', 'AnyDesk', 'Connect to a computer remotely, be it from the other end of the office or halfway around the world.
AnyDesk ensures secure and reliable remote desktop connections for IT professionals and on-the-go individuals alike.', 'Office', 'anydesksoftwaregmbh-anydesk-icon', ''),
('anylogic-anylogic-personal', 'Anylogic Personal Learning Edition', 'AnyLogic is a multimethod, java-based simulation modeling tool developed by The AnyLogic Company. It supports agent-based, discrete event, and system dynamics simulation methodologies.', 'Development', 'anylogic-anylogic-personal-icon', ''),
('anylogic-anylogic-professional', 'Anylogic Professional', 'AnyLogic is a multimethod, java-based simulation modeling tool developed by The AnyLogic Company. It supports agent-based, discrete event, and system dynamics simulation methodologies.', 'Development', 'anylogic-anylogic-professional-icon', ''),
('anylogic-anylogic-university', 'Anylogic University', 'AnyLogic is a multimethod, java-based simulation modeling tool developed by The AnyLogic Company. It supports agent-based, discrete event, and system dynamics simulation methodologies.', 'Development', 'anylogic-anylogic-university-icon', ''),
('anytxt-anytxtsearcher', 'AnyTXT Searcher', 'AnyTXT Searcher is a free powerful local document & text search application, just like a local disk Google search engine, and much faster than Windows search and Windows findstr command. Anytxt is your best free desktop file content full-text search engine.', 'Office', 'anytxt-anytxtsearcher-icon', ''),
('anydo-anydo', 'Anydo', 'Organize your tasks, lists and reminders in Any.do app.', 'Utilities', 'anydo-anydo-icon', ''),
('apache-directorystudio', 'Apache Directory Studio', 'Apache Directory Studio is a complete directory tooling platform intended to be used with any LDAP server however it is particularly designed for use with ApacheDS. It is an Eclipse RCP application, composed of several Eclipse (OSGi) plugins, that can be easily upgraded with additional ones. These plugins can even run within Eclipse itself.', 'Design', 'apache-directorystudio-icon', ''),
('apache-groovy-2-5', 'Groovy 2.5', 'Groovy is a powerful multi-faceted programming language for the JVM platform. It supports a spectrum of programming styles incorporating features from dynamic languages such as optional and duck typing, but also static compilation and static type checking at levels similar to or greater than Java through its extensible static type checker. It aims to greatly increase developer productivity with many powerful features but also a concise, familiar and easy to learn syntax.', 'Development', 'apache-groovy-2-5-icon', ''),
('apache-groovy-3', 'Groovy 3', 'Groovy is a powerful multi-faceted programming language for the JVM platform. It supports a spectrum of programming styles incorporating features from dynamic languages such as optional and duck typing, but also static compilation and static type checking at levels similar to or greater than Java through its extensible static type checker. It aims to greatly increase developer productivity with many powerful features but also a concise, familiar and easy to learn syntax.', 'Development', 'apache-groovy-3-icon', ''),
('apache-groovy-4', 'Groovy 4', 'Groovy is a powerful multi-faceted programming language for the JVM platform. It supports a spectrum of programming styles incorporating features from dynamic languages such as optional and duck typing, but also static compilation and static type checking at levels similar to or greater than Java through its extensible static type checker. It aims to greatly increase developer productivity with many powerful features but also a concise, familiar and easy to learn syntax.', 'Development', 'apache-groovy-4-icon', ''),
('apache-openoffice', 'OpenOffice', 'Apache OpenOffice is the leading open-source office software suite for word processing, spreadsheets, presentations, graphics, databases and more. It is available in many languages and works on all common computers. It stores all your data in an international open standard format and can also read and write files from other common office software packages. It can be downloaded and used completely free of charge for any purpose.', 'Development', 'apache-openoffice-icon', ''),
('apachefriends-xampp-7-4', 'XAMPP 7.4', 'XAMPP is an easy to install Apache distribution containing MariaDB, PHP and Perl.', 'Development', 'apachefriends-xampp-7-4-icon', ''),
('apachefriends-xampp-8-0', 'XAMPP 8.0', 'XAMPP is an easy to install Apache distribution containing MariaDB, PHP and Perl.', 'Development', 'apachefriends-xampp-8-0-icon', ''),
('apachefriends-xampp-8-1', 'XAMPP 8.1', 'XAMPP is an easy to install Apache distribution containing MariaDB, PHP and Perl.', 'Development', 'apachefriends-xampp-8-1-icon', ''),
('apachefriends-xampp-8-2', 'XAMPP 8.2', 'XAMPP is an easy to install Apache distribution containing MariaDB, PHP and Perl.', 'Development', 'apachefriends-xampp-8-2-icon', ''),
('apifox-apifox', 'Apifox', 'Apifox is an all-in-one collaboration platform for API documentation, API debugging, API Mock and API test automation, positioning Postman + Swagger + Mock + JMeter. With one system and one data, it solves data sync problems among multiple systems. As long as the API documentation is defined, API debugging, API data Mock, API test automation can be used directly without the need to redefine; API documentation shares the same tool with API development and debugging, so once the API debugging is completed, it can be ensured that it is identical to the definition of the API documentation. Efficient, timely and accurate!', 'Development', 'apifox-apifox-icon', ''),
('appwork-jdownloader', 'JDownloader 2', 'JDownloader is a free, open-source download management tool with a huge community of developers that makes downloading as easy and fast as it should be. Users can start, stop or pause  downloads, set bandwith limitations, auto-extract archives and much more.
', 'Development', 'appwork-jdownloader-icon', ''),
('appbytroye-koodoreader', 'Koodo Reader', 'Koodo Reader is an all-in-one ebook reader that can help you better manage and study your ebooks.
It''s free and open-source.', 'Office', 'appbytroye-koodoreader-icon', ''),
('appest-ticktick', 'TickTick', 'TickTick is a powerful to-do & task management app with seamless cloud synchronization across all your devices. Whether you need to schedule an agenda, make memos, share shopping lists, collaborate in a team, or even develop a new habit, TickTick is always here to help you get stuff done and keep life on track.', 'Development', 'appest-ticktick-icon', ''),
('apple-airport', 'AirPort', 'AirPort Installer', 'Utilities', 'apple-airport-icon', ''),
('apple-dvdorcdsharing', 'DVD or CD Sharing', 'software that enables remote disc sharing, system software restoration, and wireless migration with MacBook Air.', 'Utilities', 'apple-dvdorcdsharing-icon', ''),
('apple-proresrawforwindows', 'ProRes RAW for Windows', 'Apple ProRes on PC', 'Utilities', 'apple-proresrawforwindows-icon', ''),
('apple-windowsmigrationassistant', 'Windows Migration Assistant', 'Windows Migration Assistant Installer', 'Utilities', 'apple-windowsmigrationassistant-icon', ''),
('apple-itunes', 'iTunes', 'iTunes is a media player developed by Apple that also can be used to communicate with Apple mobile devices', 'Development', 'apple-itunes-icon', 'Rhythmbox / Strawberry'),
('approximatrix-simplyfortran', 'Simply Fortran 3', 'Simply Fortran is a complete Fortran solution for Microsoft Windows. The package includes a configured Fortran compiler installation, an integrated development environment, and a graphical debugger.', 'Development', 'approximatrix-simplyfortran-icon', ''),
('apreltech-hvmanager', 'HvManager', 'Virtual machine manager for Hyper-v designed as a web browser app.', 'Design', 'apreltech-hvmanager-icon', ''),
('apreltech-powermanager', 'Power Manager', 'Power manager is a tool designed to configure and schedule PC power management actions.', 'Design', 'apreltech-powermanager-icon', ''),
('apreltech-silentinstallbuilder', 'Silent Install Builder', 'The Silent Install Builder is a great tool if you need to quickly install a set of software on a multiple computers.', 'Utilities', 'apreltech-silentinstallbuilder-icon', ''),
('apreltech-silentinstallbuilder-beta', 'Silent Install Builder Beta', 'The Silent Install Builder is a great tool if you need to quickly install a set of software on a multiple computers.', 'Utilities', 'apreltech-silentinstallbuilder-beta-icon', ''),
('arcaderenegade-sidebardiagnostics', 'Sidebar Diagnostics', 'A simple sidebar for Windows desktop that displays hardware diagnostic information.', 'Development', 'arcaderenegade-sidebardiagnostics-icon', ''),
('arctype-arctype', 'Arctype', 'Arctype is a fast, beautiful database GUI for developers and teams. With SQL autocomplete, spreadsheet-style editing, one-click visualizations, collaboration, and the best support for Postgres, MySQL, and PlanetScale - you''ll finally love working with your DB.', 'Development', 'arctype-arctype-icon', ''),
('arduinosa-ide-beta', 'Arduino IDE Beta', 'The open-source Arduino Software (IDE) makes it easy to write code and upload it to the board. This software can be used with any Arduino board.', 'Development', 'arduinosa-ide-beta-icon', ''),
('arduinosa-ide-rc', 'Arduino IDE RC', 'An integrated development environment for Arduino microcontroller boards and compatibles (release candidate version)', 'Development', 'arduinosa-ide-rc-icon', ''),
('arduinosa-ide-stable', 'Arduino IDE', 'An integrated development environment for Arduino microcontroller boards and compatibles', 'Development', 'arduinosa-ide-stable-icon', ''),
('argotronic-argusmonitor', 'Argus Monitor', 'Fan speed control based on all available temperature sources, like HDD/SSD or GPU temperatures.', 'Utilities', 'argotronic-argusmonitor-icon', ''),
('aries-sciences-llc-ai-chess', 'Dr. Henry''s Chess Game', 'This is a cross-platform AI chess game developed by Dr. Henry and packaged by Ozan Mirza.', 'Games', 'aries-sciences-llc-ai-chess-icon', ''),
('arm-gnuarmembeddedtoolchain', 'GNU Arm Embedded Toolchain', 'The GNU Arm Embedded toolchain contains integrated and validated packages featuring the GCC compiler, libraries and other tools necessary for bare-metal software development on devices based on 32-bit Arm Cortex-A, Cortex-R and Cortex-M processors.', 'Development', 'arm-gnuarmembeddedtoolchain-icon', ''),
('armcord-armcord', 'ArmCord', 'ArmCord is a custom client designed to enhance your Discord experience while keeping everything lightweight.', 'Games', 'armcord-armcord-icon', ''),
('armagetronadvanced-armagetronadvanced', 'Armagetron Advanced', '3D multiplayer game with Tron-style lightcycles', 'Games', 'armagetronadvanced-armagetronadvanced-icon', ''),
('armin2208-windowsautonightmode', 'Auto Dark Mode', 'Automatically switches between the dark and light theme of Windows 10 and Windows 11. Auto Dark Mode helps you to be more productive. Because you shouldn''t care about changing Windows settings several times a day. As soon as the sun goes down, we''ll take care of everything for you. Because a simple design change would be too boring, Auto Dark Mode is packed with useful functions. For example, we can also change your desktop wallpaper.', 'Design', 'armin2208-windowsautonightmode-icon', ''),
('arobasmusic-guitarpro-7', 'Arobas Music', 'Advanced musical instrument tablature and scoring application', 'Audio', 'arobasmusic-guitarpro-7-icon', ''),
('artha-artha', 'Artha', 'Artha is a handy thesaurus based on WordNet with distinct features like global hotkey look-up, passive desktop notifications, regular expression based search, etc. Artha may be used as a free open-source replacement to the proprietary WordWeb Pro.', 'Design', 'artha-artha-icon', ''),
('artifexsoftware-ghostscript', 'GPL Ghostscript', 'An interpreter for the PostScript language and for PDF.', 'Office', 'artifexsoftware-ghostscript-icon', ''),
('artisteerlimited-nicepage', 'Nicepage', 'Absolute Creativity With No Coding Simple drag-and-drop website builder software to implement any ideas', 'Development', 'artisteerlimited-nicepage-icon', ''),
('artsoft-rocksndiamonds', 'Rocks''n''Diamonds', 'Arcade style game in the tradition of Boulder Dash, Emerald Mine, Supaplex and Sokoban. Featuring classic Amiga style graphics, stereo sounds and MOD music.', 'Games', 'artsoft-rocksndiamonds-icon', ''),
('asana-asana', 'Asana', 'Asana is team collaboration tool. It has list view, timeline, board feature.', 'Utilities', 'asana-asana-icon', ''),
('asaphahalifa-audiorelay', 'AudioRelay', 'AudioRelay is an application to stream every sound from your PC to one or multiple Android devices.', 'Audio', 'asaphahalifa-audiorelay-icon', ''),
('ascension-ascensionlauncher', 'Ascension Launcher', 'Project Ascension is a Classless game that allows you to imagine and build the character of your dreams. Your custom character has any ability or talent within their reach. Imagine your hero and achieve glory!', 'Games', 'ascension-ascensionlauncher-icon', ''),
('ashishbharadwajj-flawesome', 'Flawesome', 'Flawesome is a modern productivity tool that will help you organise your day-today work and thoughts.', 'Utilities', 'ashishbharadwajj-flawesome-icon', ''),
