('christiankaiser-lightscreen', 'Lightscreen', 'Lightscreen is a simple tool to automate the tedious process of saving and cataloging screenshots, it operates as a hidden background process that is invoked with one (or multiple) hotkeys and then saves a screenshot file to disk according to the user''s preferences.', 'Utilities', 'christiankaiser-lightscreen-icon', ''),
