('codesector-teracopy', 'TeraCopy', 'A popular utility designed to copy files faster and more reliably, providing the user with many features. TeraCopy uses dynamically adjusted buffers to reduce seek time. It can resume broken file transfers and skup bad files during the copying process.', 'Design', 'codesector-teracopy-icon', ''),
