('c0re100-qbittorrent-enhanced-edition', 'qBittorrent Enhanced Edition', 'qBittorrent is a bittorrent client programmed in C++ / Qt that uses libtorrent (sometimes called libtorrent-rasterbar) by Arvid Norberg. 1.
