('dell-commandconfigure', 'Dell Command | Configure', 'Dell Command | Configure is a packaged software application that provides configuration capability to business client platforms. This product consists of a Command Line Interface (CLI) and Graphical User Interface (GUI) to configure various BIOS features. Dell Command | Configure supports Windows and Linux operating systems.', 'Development', 'dell-commandconfigure-icon', ''),
('dell-commandupdate', 'Dell Command | Update', 'Dell Command Update is a stand-alone application for client systems, that provides updates for system software that is released by Dell. This application simplifies the BIOS, firmware, driver, and application update experience for Dell client hardware.', 'Development', 'dell-commandupdate-icon', ''),
('dell-commandupdate-universal', 'Dell Command | Update for Windows Universal', 'Dell Command Update is a stand-alone application for client systems, that provides updates for system software that is released by Dell. This application simplifies the BIOS, firmware, driver, and application update experience for Dell client hardware.', 'Development', 'dell-commandupdate-universal-icon', ''),
