('desksoft-earthview', 'EarthView', 'EarthView is a dynamic desktop wallpaper and screen saver, which displays beautiful views of the earth with daylight and night shadows. It produces high quality images for every screen resolution - even beyond 2560x1600! The program supports map and globe views, urban areas, city lights, atmospheric effects, clouds and much more.', 'Design', 'desksoft-earthview-icon', ''),
