('ditto-ditto', 'Ditto', 'Ditto is an extension to the standard windows clipboard. It saves each item placed on the clipboard allowing you access to any of those items at a later time.', 'Utilities', 'ditto-ditto-icon', ''),
('dixa-dixa', 'Dixa', 'Dixa Desktop app for Windows and Mac', 'Utilities', 'dixa-dixa-icon', ''),
('djvulibre-djview', 'DjVuLibre DjView', 'DjVu is a web-centric format for distributing documents and images. DjVu was created at AT&T Labs-Research and later sold to LizardTech Inc. DjVuLibre is a GPL implementation of DjVu maintained by the original inventors of DjVu.', 'Design', 'djvulibre-djview-icon', ''),
