('ducfabulous-ultraviewer', 'UltraViewer', 'UltraViewer is a software that helps you to remote control your client''s computer to support them like you''re sitting in front of the screen.', 'Utilities', 'ducfabulous-ultraviewer-icon', ''),
('dummerle-rare', 'Rare', 'Rare is a graphical interface for Legendary, a command line alternative to Epic Games launcher, based on PyQt5', 'Games', 'dummerle-rare-icon', ''),
('duosecurity-duo2faauthenticationforwindows', 'Duo Authentication for Windows Logon', 'Duo integrates with Microsoft Windows client and server operating systems to add two-factor authentication to Remote Desktop and local logons and credentialed UAC elevation prompts.', 'Utilities', 'duosecurity-duo2faauthenticationforwindows-icon', ''),
('duongdieuphap-imageglass', 'ImageGlass', 'ImageGlass is a simple picture viewer with which you will be able to display your image collection in a very similar way to the one that Windows provides by default, but with some additional functions.
This application will allow you to better manage your pictures thanks to the options it includes and the extension it enables to install for adding more functions and widening its possibilities.', 'Development', 'duongdieuphap-imageglass-icon', ''),
