('dygmalabs-bazecor', 'Bazecor', 'The Bazecor configurator software allows you to remap any key and create up to 10 fully programmable layers for your Dygma Raise keyboard. It also allows you to create and manage superkeys, macros, and shortcuts.', 'Utilities', 'dygmalabs-bazecor-icon', ''),
