Available actions: Shutdown, Reboot, Log Off, Lock Workstation, Sleep, Hibernate, Turn Off Monitor, Screen Saver, Volume Control, Hang Up Modem, Alarm, Message, Play Sound, Run Program, Open File, Close Window, Kill Process.
Desktop links can be created to execute any of the supported actions directly from desktop. Web Interface allows remote execution of actions and displays run-time information about the computer: Up Time, List of Processes, Screenshot of a Desktop, Program Execution, and more.', 'Audio', 'den4b-shutter-icon', ''),
('deskfiler-deskfiler', 'Deskfiler', 'An Open Source electron plugin ecosystem for JS developers that makes tools for the desktop on Windows, Mac and Linux easily deployable and manageable as plugins.', 'Development', 'deskfiler-deskfiler-icon', ''),
