or the built-in control panel. You can even record and log MIDI data and then convert it to a Standard MIDI File for playback by a sequencer.', 'Utilities', 'jamieoconnell-midi-ox-icon', ''),
('jamiepine-cachemonkey', 'CacheMonkey', 'Images you see online are never deleted immediately, unless you delete them of course. Most desktop apps have a cache directory, not all provide the tools to clear it. CacheMonkey not only lets you purge cache files, but browse and filter through them too.', 'Development', 'jamiepine-cachemonkey-icon', ''),
('jandedobbeleer-ohmyposh', 'Oh My Posh', 'Prompt theme engine for any shell', 'Development', 'jandedobbeleer-ohmyposh-icon', ''),
('janfiala-pspad', 'PSpad editor', 'PSPad is a freeware programmer''s editor for Microsoft Windows operating systems', 'Development', 'janfiala-pspad-icon', ''),
('jangrzegorowski-timeseriesadmin', 'Time Series Admin', 'Administration and querying interface for InfluxDB databases', 'Development', 'jangrzegorowski-timeseriesadmin-icon', ''),
('janjoneš-ipasim', 'ipaSim', 'iOS emulator for Windows', 'Utilities', 'janjoneš-ipasim-icon', ''),
('janprochazka-dbgate', 'DbGate', 'Database manager for MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQL Server, MongoDB, SQLite and others. Runs under Windows, Linux, Mac or as web application', 'Development', 'janprochazka-dbgate-icon', ''),
('jannisx11-blockbench', 'Blockbench', 'Blockbench is a free, modern model editor for boxy models and pixel art textures. Models can be exported for Minecraft Java and Bedrock Edition as well as most game engines and other 3D applications. Blockbench features a modern and intuitive UI, plugin support and innovative features. It is the industry standard for creating custom 3D models for the Minecraft Marketplace.', 'Games', 'jannisx11-blockbench-icon', ''),
('jaquadro-nbtexplorer', 'NBTExplorer', 'A graphical NBT editor for all Minecraft NBT data sources.', 'Design', 'jaquadro-nbtexplorer-icon', ''),
('jasmine-nova', 'Nova', 'Nova is a CLI for controlling Govee light strips.', 'Utilities', 'jasmine-nova-icon', ''),
('jasnapaka-mozbackup', 'MozBackup', 'MozBackup is a simple utility for creating backups of Mozilla Firefox, Mozilla Thunderbird, Mozilla Sunbird, Flock, SeaMonkey, Mozilla Suite, Spicebird, Songbird and Netscape profiles.', 'Utilities', 'jasnapaka-mozbackup-icon', ''),
('jasonwei512-code-radio-cli', 'code-radio-cli', 'A command line music radio client for https://coderadio.freecodecamp.org', 'Development', 'jasonwei512-code-radio-cli-icon', ''),
