('jetbrains-fleetlauncher-eap', 'Fleet Launcher (Early Access Program)', 'You can install JetBrains Fleet on a remote machine for remote development. This addresses the case when you have a powerful box at home or in the office, and you want to use your local workstation as a thin client. This approach allows you to leverage higher compute capacity and avoid running heavy tasks locally.', 'Games', 'jetbrains-fleetlauncher-eap-icon', ''),
