('jetbrains-youtrack', 'JetBrains YouTrack', 'Enjoy having everything together in one place. Track tasks, manage projects, keep a knowledge base, collaborate with your team, and deliver great products. Designed with all the members of your team in mind. Free for teams of 10. In our cloud or on your server.', 'Development', 'jetbrains-youtrack-icon', ''),
