('jidifudi-gt4t', 'GT4T', 'GT4T is an automatic translation application that runs on Windows/Mac. With GT4T, you can get translation suggestions for selected content in any window, as well as batch translate documents in Office, PDF, CAT, and Markdown/AsciDoc/reStructedText formats.', 'Office', 'jidifudi-gt4t-icon', ''),
