('memurai-memuraideveloper', 'Memurai Developer', 'It is designed to provide the reliability and performance demanded by enterprise Windows environments.
Just like Redis, Memurai uses an in-memory data set to achieve great performance at scale,
and Memurai supports all the Redis features that you know and love, such as persistence,
replication, transactions, LUA scripting, high-availability, pub/sub, cluster, modules, streams, and LRU eviction.
In fact, it supports all of the Redis API 5 eviction policies.', 'Development', 'memurai-memuraideveloper-icon', ''),
('mercurial-mercurial', 'Mercurial', 'Mercurial is a distributed revision control tool for software developers.', 'Development', 'mercurial-mercurial-icon', ''),
('meshhouse-meshhouse', 'MeshHouse', 'Open-source program for catalogizing 3d models', 'Design', 'meshhouse-meshhouse-icon', ''),
('metageek-inssider', 'inSSIDer', 'Tool to analyze surrounding wifi networks', 'Development', 'metageek-inssider-icon', ''),
('miktex-miktex', 'MiKTeX', 'MiKTeX is a modern TeX distribution for Windows.', 'Utilities', 'miktex-miktex-icon', ''),
('mixxx-mixxx', 'mixxx', 'Mixxx is Free DJ software that gives you everything you need to perform live DJ mixes. Mixxx works on GNU/Linux, Windows, and macOS.', 'Utilities', 'mixxx-mixxx-icon', ''),
('micaforeveryone-micaforeveryone', 'Mica For Everyone', 'a tool to enable backdrop effect on titlebar of win32 apps on Windows 11', 'Utilities', 'micaforeveryone-micaforeveryone-icon', ''),
('michaelbromley-skqw', 'SKQW', 'A desktop audio visualizer, built with Electron and Angular', 'Audio', 'michaelbromley-skqw-icon', ''),
('michaeldicarlo-postybirb', 'PostyBirb', 'PostyBirb is an application that helps artists post art and other multimedia to multiple websites more quickly.', 'Design', 'michaeldicarlo-postybirb-icon', ''),
('michaeltippach-asio4all', 'ASIO4ALL', 'Low latency ASIO driver for Windows audio', 'Audio', 'michaeltippach-asio4all-icon', ''),
('microsip-microsip', 'MicroSIP', 'It allowing to do high quality VoIP calls (person-to-person or on regular telephones) via open SIP protocol. From cloud of SIP providers you can choose best for you, register account and use it with MicroSIP. You''ll get free person-to-person calls and cheap international calls.', 'Development', 'microsip-microsip-icon', ''),
('microsip-microsip-lite', 'MicroSIP Lite', 'It allowing to do high quality VoIP calls (person-to-person or on regular telephones) via open SIP protocol. From cloud of SIP providers you can choose best for you, register account and use it with MicroSIP. You''ll get free person-to-person calls and cheap international calls.', 'Development', 'microsip-microsip-lite-icon', ''),
('microsoft-adkpeaddon', 'Windows Assessment and Deployment Kit Windows Preinstallation Environment Add-ons', 'The Windows Preinstallation Environment addon for the Windows ADK.', 'Utilities', 'microsoft-adkpeaddon-icon', ''),
('microsoft-appinstallerfilebuilder', 'AppInstaller File Builder(Preview)', 'AppInstaller File Builder is a Windows 10 application for users to easily build an AppInstaller file.', 'Development', 'microsoft-appinstallerfilebuilder-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azd', 'Azure Developer CLI', 'A developer CLI that accelerates the time it takes for you to get started on Azure. The Azure Developer CLI (azd) provides a set of developer-friendly commands that map to key stages in your workflow - code, build, deploy, monitor, repeat.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azd-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-azcopy-10', 'AzCopy v10', 'AzCopy v10 is a command-line utility that you can use to copy data to and from containers and file shares in Azure Storage accounts. AzCopy V10 presents easy-to-use commands that are optimized for high performance and throughput.', 'Utilities', 'microsoft-azure-azcopy-10-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-aztfexport', 'Microsoft Azure Export for Terraform', 'Microsoft Azure Export for Terraform imports the resources that are supported by the Terraform AzureRM provider into the Terraform state, and generates the corresponding Terraform configuration.
Both the Terraform state and configuration are expected to be consistent with the resources'' remote state, i.e., terraform plan shows no diff.
The user then is able to use Terraform to manage these resources.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-aztfexport-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-aztfy', 'Azure Terrafy', 'Azure Terrafy imports the resources that are supported by the Terraform AzureRM provider into the Terraform state, and generates the corresponding Terraform configuration.
Both the Terraform state and configuration are expected to be consistent with the resources'' remote state, i.e., terraform plan shows no diff.
The user then is able to use Terraform to manage these resources.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-aztfy-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-cosmosemulator', 'Azure Cosmos DB Emulator', 'The Azure Cosmos emulator provides a local environment that emulates the Azure Cosmos DB service for development purposes.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-cosmosemulator-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-datacli', 'Azure Data CLI', 'A command-line utility written in Python to bootstrap and manage the data services via REST APIs', 'Utilities', 'microsoft-azure-datacli-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-functionscoretools', 'Azure Functions Core Tools', 'The Azure Functions Core Tools provide a local development experience for creating, developing, testing, running, and debugging Azure Functions.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-functionscoretools-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-iotexplorer', 'Azure IoT Explorer Preview', 'Cross-platform UI for interacting with devices attached to Azure IoT Hub', 'Utilities', 'microsoft-azure-iotexplorer-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-kubelogin', 'Microsoft Azure Kubelogin', 'kubelogin is a client-go credential (exec) plugin implementing azure authentication. This plugin provides features that are not available in kubectl. It is supported on kubectl v1.11+', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-kubelogin-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-storageemulator', 'Microsoft Azure Storage Emulator', 'The Microsoft Azure Storage Emulator is a tool that emulates the Azure Blob, Queue, and Table services for local development purposes.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azure-storageemulator-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azure-storageexplorer', 'Microsoft Azure Storage Explorer', 'Free tool to easily manage your Azure cloud storage resources anywhere, from Windows, macOS, or Linux.', 'Utilities', 'microsoft-azure-storageexplorer-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azurecli', 'Microsoft Azure CLI', 'The Azure command-line interface (Azure CLI) is a set of commands used to create and manage Azure resources. The Azure CLI is available across Azure services and is designed to get you working quickly with Azure, with an emphasis on automation.', 'Design', 'microsoft-azurecli-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azuredatastudio', 'Azure Data Studio', 'Azure Data Studio is a data management tool that enables you to work with SQL Server, Azure SQL DB and SQL DW from Windows, macOS and Linux.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azuredatastudio-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azuredatastudio-insiders', 'Azure Data Studio - Insiders', 'Azure Data Studio is a data management tool that enables you to work with SQL Server, Azure SQL DB and SQL DW from Windows, macOS and Linux.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azuredatastudio-insiders-icon', ''),
('microsoft-azuremediaservicesexplorer', 'Azure Media Services Explorer', 'Azure Media Services Explorer is a test tool for Windows that provides upload, download, process, encode, package, and stream assets and live events with Azure Media Services using the AMS .Net SDK and the REST API. Source code is also provided on GitHub.', 'Development', 'microsoft-azuremediaservicesexplorer-icon', ''),
('microsoft-bicep', 'Bicep CLI', 'Bicep is a Domain Specific Language (DSL) for deploying Azure resources declaratively. It aims to drastically simplify the authoring experience with a cleaner syntax and better support for modularity and code re-use.', 'Development', 'microsoft-bicep-icon', ''),
('microsoft-bingwallpaper', 'Bing Wallpaper', 'Bing Wallpaper includes a collection of beautiful images from around the world that have been featured on the Bing homepage. Not only will you see a new image on your desktop each day, but you can also browse images and learn where they''re from.', 'Design', 'microsoft-bingwallpaper-icon', ''),
('microsoft-botframeworkcomposer', 'Bot Framework Composer', 'Bot Framework Composer is an integrated development tool for developers and multi-disciplinary teams to build bots and conversational experiences with the Microsoft Bot Framework. Within this tool, you''ll find everything you need to build a sophisticated conversational experience.', 'Development', 'microsoft-botframeworkcomposer-icon', ''),
('microsoft-botframeworkemulator', 'Bot Framework Emulator', 'Development tool for the Microsoft Bot Framework. Allows developers to test and debug bots on localhost.', 'Development', 'microsoft-botframeworkemulator-icon', ''),
('microsoft-buildtools2015', 'Microsoft Build Tools 2015', 'Microsoft Build Tools 2015 provides the essential tools for building managed applications. These tools previously were included in the .NET Framework, but they are now available as this separate download.', 'Development', 'microsoft-buildtools2015-icon', ''),
('microsoft-clrtypessqlserver-2019', 'Microsoft System CLR Types for SQL Server 2019', 'The SQL Server System CLR Types package contains the components implementing the geometry, geography, and hierarchy ID types in SQL Server', 'Development', 'microsoft-clrtypessqlserver-2019-icon', ''),
('microsoft-deploymenttoolkit', 'Microsoft Deployment Toolkit', 'Microsoft Deployment Toolkit (MDT) provides a unified collection of tools, processes, and guidance for automating desktop and server deployments.', 'Development', 'microsoft-deploymenttoolkit-icon', ''),
('microsoft-directx', 'DirectX End-User Runtime Web Installer', 'The Microsoft DirectX® End-User Runtime installs a number of runtime libraries from the legacy DirectX SDK for some games that use D3DX9, D3DX10, D3DX11, XAudio 2.7, XInput 1.3, XACT, and/or Managed DirectX 1.1. Note that this package does not modify the DirectX Runtime installed on your Windows OS in any way.', 'Games', 'microsoft-directx-icon', ''),
