('nevcairiel-lavfilters', 'LAV Filters', 'LAV Filters are a set of DirectShow filters based on the libavformat and libavcodec libraries from the ffmpeg project, which will allow you to play virtually any format in a DirectShow player.', 'Development', 'nevcairiel-lavfilters-icon', ''),
('newbreedsoftware-tuxpaint', 'Tux Paint', 'Tux Paint is a free, award-winning drawing program for children ages 3 to 12 (for example, preschool and K-6). Tux Paint is used in schools around the world as a computer literacy drawing activity. It combines an easy-to-use interface, fun sound effects, and an encouraging cartoon mascot who guides children as they use the program.', 'Development', 'newbreedsoftware-tuxpaint-icon', ''),
