('nextdns-nextdns-cli', 'NextDNS CLI', 'NextDNS CLI is a DNS53 to DNS-over-HTTPS (DoH) proxy with advanced capabilities to get
the most out of the NextDNS service. Although the most advanced features will only work
with NextDNS, this program can work as a client for any DoH provider or a mix of NextDNS
