('ncyxie-notepad-dot-qt', 'Notepad DOT Qt', 'Notepad DOT Qt is an open-source, cross-platform and highly customizable text editor. It has all essential notepad functions with more handy stuff. It is suitable for daily driving, from newbies to advanced users.', 'Design', 'ncyxie-notepad-dot-qt-icon', ''),
