('octopusdeploy-server', 'Octopus Deploy Server', 'Octopus Deploy makes it easy to automate your deployments and operations runbooks from a single place, helping you ship code faster, improve reliability, and break down dev & ops silos.', 'Development', 'octopusdeploy-server-icon', ''),
