('onescript-onescript', 'OneScript engine', 'OneScript engine', 'Utilities', 'onescript-onescript-icon', ''),
('onetagger-onetagger', 'One Tagger', 'Cross-platform music tagger. It can fetch metadata from Beatport, Traxsource, Juno Download, Discogs, Musicbrainz and Spotify. It is also able to fetch Spotify''s Audio Features based on ISRC & exact match. There is a manual tag editor and quick tag editor which lets you use keyboard shortcuts. Written in Rust, Vue.js and Quasar. MP3, AIFF, FLAC, M4A (AAC, ALAC) supported. For more info and tutorials check out our website.', 'Audio', 'onetagger-onetagger-icon', ''),
('onionshare-onionshare', 'OnionShare', 'OnionShare lets you securely and anonymously share files of any size.
It works by starting a web server, making it accessible as a Tor onion service, and generating an unguessable URL to access and download the files.
It doesn''t require setting up a server on the internet somewhere or using a third party file-sharing service.
You host the file on your own computer and use a Tor onion service to make it temporarily accessible over the internet.
The other user just needs to use Tor Browser to download the file from you.', 'Design', 'onionshare-onionshare-icon', ''),
('onionshare-onionshare-dev', 'OnionShare Dev', 'OnionShare lets you securely and anonymously share files of any size.
It works by starting a web server, making it accessible as a Tor onion service, and generating an unguessable URL to access and download the files.
It doesn''t require setting up a server on the internet somewhere or using a third party file-sharing service.
You host the file on your own computer and use a Tor onion service to make it temporarily accessible over the internet.
The other user just needs to use Tor Browser to download the file from you.', 'Design', 'onionshare-onionshare-dev-icon', ''),
('onlinemediatechnologiesltd-avsdisccreator', 'AVS Disc Creator', 'AVS Disc Creator is a compact and fully functional application that lets you perform different burning tasks with any kind of files.', 'Utilities', 'onlinemediatechnologiesltd-avsdisccreator-icon', ''),
('ookla-speedtest-cli', 'Speedtest CLI', 'Internet connection measurement for developers', 'Development', 'ookla-speedtest-cli-icon', ''),
('ookla-speedtest-desktop', 'Speedtest by Ookla', 'Speedtest® by Ookla® is the definitive way to test the speed and performance of your internet connection.
Every day, over ten million unique tests are actively initiated by our users in the locations and at the times when their connectivity matters to them.
Since our founding in 2006, an unparalleled total of more than 40 billion tests have been taken with Speedtest.', 'Utilities', 'ookla-speedtest-desktop-icon', ''),
