('openlivewriter-openlivewriter', 'Open Live Writer', 'Open Live Writer makes it easy to write, preview and post to your blog.', 'Utilities', 'openlivewriter-openlivewriter-icon', ''),
('openmpt-openmpt', 'OpenMPT', 'OpenMPT is being developed since 1997 (initially named ModPlug Tracker) and can be used as a "classic" sample-based tracker to edit and play your favourite tracked music, but also as a modern DAW with plugin support and other great features. Here, you can find some of the key features of the tracker.', 'Development', 'openmpt-openmpt-icon', ''),
