('openvpntechnologies-openvpn', 'OpenVPN', 'OpenVPN provides flexible VPN solutions to secure your data communications, whether its for Internet privacy, remote access for employees, securing IoT, or for networking Cloud data centers.', 'Development', 'openvpntechnologies-openvpn-icon', ''),
