('samsung-dex', 'Samsung DeX', 'Samsung offers many applications to make your work day easier. One of them is Samsung DeX, which gives users the experience of working on a desktop by connecting their mobile device (a smartphone or tablet) to an external display device (a TV or monitor) or a PC.', 'Design', 'samsung-dex-icon', ''),
