Have you always wanted your notes from junior year as a category in steam? If so that''s pretty weird! But now it''s possible.', 'Games', 'steamgriddb-rommanager-icon', ''),
('steccas-protonclient', 'ProtonClient', 'An unofficial desktop client for ProtonMail done with electron nativefier. I just did it because I didnt want to open the browser every time I wanted to check my protonmail, I dont like to use Proton Bridge which is buggy and I prefer to access protonmail without an intermediary software while keeping desktop notifications and a dedicated app.', 'Utilities', 'steccas-protonclient-icon', ''),
