('stefansundin-superf4', 'SuperF4', 'Hard kills programs similar to the task manager using Alt+F4. Useful for unstable programs. Not my property but has been brought here for your convienence.', 'Utilities', 'stefansundin-superf4-icon', ''),
('stefanstools-bowpad', 'BowPad', 'BowPad is a small and fast text editor with a ribbon user interface and syntax highlighting.', 'Design', 'stefanstools-bowpad-icon', ''),
