('strawberrymusicplayer-strawberry', 'Strawberry Music Player', 'Strawberry is a cross-platform music player written in C++, which can also be used to organize smaller and larger music collections.', 'Audio', 'strawberrymusicplayer-strawberry-icon', ''),
('strawberryperl-strawberryperl', 'Strawberry Perl', 'Perl is a programming language suitable for writing simple scripts as well as complex applications - see https://www.perl.org

Strawberry Perl is a perl environment for MS Windows containing all you need to run and develop perl applications. It is designed to be as close as possible to perl environment on UNIX systems.

