('stream-pi-server', 'Stream-Pi Server', 'An Opensource, Cross-Platform, Programmable, Modular Macropad Software', 'Utilities', 'stream-pi-server-icon', ''),
('streamlabs-streamlabs', 'Streamlabs Desktop', 'Streamlabs is a live streaming app that integrates OBS Studio with viewer interactions, chat management, and tip donations.
Streamlabs uses OBS Studio for media streaming and Electron for user interface.
Streamlabs distributes their users content over platforms such as Twitch, YouTube Live, and Facebook Live.', 'Games', 'streamlabs-streamlabs-icon', ''),
