('splode-pomotroid', 'Pomotroid', 'Pomotroid is a simple and configurable Pomodoro timer. It aims to provide a visually-pleasing and reliable way to track productivity using the Pomodoro Technique.', 'Development', 'splode-pomotroid-icon', ''),
