('stackless-stackless', 'Stackless Python', 'Stackless Python is an enhanced version of the Python programming language. It allows programmers to reap the benefits of thread-based programming without the performance and complexity problems associated with conventional threads.', 'Development', 'stackless-stackless-icon', ''),
