('staniel359-muffon', 'muffon', 'muffon is a desktop music browser / streaming service that retrieves info and audio/video from Last.FM, Discogs, VK, YouTube, Deezer, Yandex Music, Odnoklassniki, Spotify, SoundCloud, Bandcamp, and Genius.

