('suse-rancherdesktop', 'Rancher Desktop', 'Rancher Desktop is an open-source project to bring Kubernetes and container management to the desktop. Windows, macOS and Linux versions of Rancher Desktop are available for download, though do note that the Linux version is considered a tech preview.', 'Development', 'suse-rancherdesktop-icon', ''),
