('tarasovartyom-batterymode', 'Battery Mode', 'Replaces Windows default battery indicator to a more powerful and useful one. It provides backlight control, easy power scheme selection, detailed battery information and a lot of handy features for customization.', 'Development', 'tarasovartyom-batterymode-icon', ''),
('tarma-publishorperish', 'Harzing''s Publish or Perish', 'Publish or Perish is a software program that retrieves and analyzes academic citations. It uses various publicly available data sources to obtain the raw citations, then analyzes these and calculates a series of citation metrics. The results are available on-screen and can also be copied to the Windows clipboard (for pasting into other applications) or saved to a text file (for future reference or further analysis).', 'Design', 'tarma-publishorperish-icon', ''),
('task-task', 'Task', 'Task is a task runner / build tool that aims to be simpler and easier to use than, for example, GNU Make.', 'Utilities', 'task-task-icon', ''),
('taskcadeinc-taskade', 'Taskade', 'Taskade is a collaborative task list with unlimited hierarchy, designed to help remote teams work together in one unified workspace.', 'Development', 'taskcadeinc-taskade-icon', ''),
('tauri-create-tauri-app', 'create-tauri-app', 'Rapidly scaffold out a new tauri app project.', 'Utilities', 'tauri-create-tauri-app-icon', ''),
('tautulli-tautulli', 'Tautulli', 'A Python based monitoring and tracking tool for Plex Media Server.', 'Utilities', 'tautulli-tautulli-icon', ''),
('texstudio-texstudio', 'TeXstudio', 'TeXstudio is a fully featured LaTeX editor. Our goal is to make writing LaTeX documents as easy and comfortable as possible. Some of the outstanding features of TeXstudio are an integrated pdf viewer with (almost) word-level synchronization, live inline preview, advanced syntax-highlighting, live checking of references, citations, latex commands, spelling and grammar. Find out more at our website.', 'Development', 'texstudio-texstudio-icon', ''),
('teaspeak-teaclient', 'TeaSpeak - Client', 'TeaClient Setup', 'Utilities', 'teaspeak-teaclient-icon', ''),
('teamdrivesystems-teamdrive', 'TeamDrive', 'TeamDrive offers fast, secure, end-to-end encrypted storage for all of your files. Your files can be safely and securely accessed and synchronized via Windows, Mac OS X and Linux desktop and tablet PC devices as well as iOS and Android mobile devices.', 'Utilities', 'teamdrivesystems-teamdrive-icon', ''),
('teamlidarr-lidarr', 'Lidarr', 'Looks and smells like Sonarr but made for music.', 'Audio', 'teamlidarr-lidarr-icon', ''),
('teamprowlarr-prowlarr', 'Prowlarr', 'Prowlarr is an indexer manager/proxy built on the popular *arr .net/reactjs base stack to integrate with your various PVR apps.
Prowlarr supports management of both Torrent Trackers and Usenet Indexers.
It integrates seamlessly with Lidarr, Mylar3, Radarr, Readarr, and Sonarr offering complete management of your indexers with no per app Indexer setup required (we do it all).', 'Utilities', 'teamprowlarr-prowlarr-icon', ''),
('teamradarr-radarr', 'Radarr', 'Radarr is a movie collection manager for Usenet and BitTorrent users.', 'Utilities', 'teamradarr-radarr-icon', ''),
('teamshinkansen-hakchi2-ce', 'Hakchi2 CE', 'The Community Edition fork of Hakchi2 from ClusterM', 'Utilities', 'teamshinkansen-hakchi2-ce-icon', ''),
('teamsonarr-sonarr', 'Sonarr', 'Sonarr is a PVR for Usenet and BitTorrent users. It can monitor multiple RSS feeds for new episodes of your favorite shows and will grab, sort and rename them.', 'Utilities', 'teamsonarr-sonarr-icon', ''),
('teamsophia-sophiapp', 'SophiApp', 'The most powerful open source tweaker on GitHub for fine-tuning Windows 10 & Windows 11.', 'Development', 'teamsophia-sophiapp-icon', ''),
('teamspeaksystems-teamspeakclient', 'TeamSpeak 3 Client', 'Use crystal clear sound to communicate with your team mates cross-platform with military-grade security, lag-free performance & unparalleled reliability and uptime.', 'Games', 'teamspeaksystems-teamspeakclient-icon', ''),
('teamviewer-teamviewer', 'TeamViewer', 'TeamViewer is a comprehensive, remote access, remote control and remote support solution that works with almost every desktop and mobile platform, including Windows, macOS, Android, and iOS.

TeamViewer lets you remote in to computers or mobile devices located anywhere in the world and use them as though you were there.', 'Utilities', 'teamviewer-teamviewer-icon', 'RustDesk / AnyDesk'),
('teamviewer-teamviewer-host', 'TeamViewer Host', 'TeamViewer is a comprehensive, remote access, remote control and remote support solution that works with almost every desktop and mobile platform, including Windows, macOS, Android, and iOS.
TeamViewer lets you remote in to computers or mobile devices located anywhere in the world and use them as though you were there.', 'Utilities', 'teamviewer-teamviewer-host-icon', 'RustDesk / AnyDesk'),
('techpowerup-gpu-z', 'TechPowerUp GPU-Z', 'GPU-Z is a lightweight system utility designed to provide vital information about your video card and graphics processor.', 'Development', 'techpowerup-gpu-z-icon', ''),
('techpowerup-nvcleanstall', 'NVCleanstall', 'NVCleanstall lets you customize the NVIDIA GeForce Driver package by removing components that you don''t need (or want). This not only keeps things tidy, but also lowers disk usage and memory footprint.', 'Utilities', 'techpowerup-nvcleanstall-icon', ''),
('techsmith-camtasia', 'Camtasia', 'Camtasia is a video-based screen capture program that enables users to demonstrate and communicate ideas or share knowledge using video. From quick video demos to extensive video projects, Camtasia has a wide range of editing tools to create video content from a variety of sources. Users can record from webcam or screen, introduce a variety of effects, and easily share videos over multiple channels.', 'Development', 'techsmith-camtasia-icon', ''),
('techsmith-snagit-2020', 'Snagit 2020', 'Screen Capture and Recording Software', 'Development', 'techsmith-snagit-2020-icon', ''),
('techsmith-snagit-2021', 'Snagit 2021', 'Screen Capture and Recording Software', 'Development', 'techsmith-snagit-2021-icon', ''),
('techsmith-snagit-2022', 'Snagit 2022', 'Screen Capture and Recording Software', 'Development', 'techsmith-snagit-2022-icon', ''),
('techsmith-snagit-2023', 'Snagit 2023', 'Snagit helps you quickly share information in a way that''s easy to understand. Capture your screen and camera, add additional context and move work forward faster.', 'Development', 'techsmith-snagit-2023-icon', ''),
('telegram-telegramdesktop', 'Telegram Desktop', 'Telegram is a cloud-based mobile and desktop messaging app with a focus on security and speed.', 'Social', 'telegram-telegramdesktop-icon', ''),
('telegram-telegramdesktop-beta', 'Telegram Desktop Beta', 'Telegram is a cloud-based mobile and desktop messaging app with a focus on security and speed.', 'Social', 'telegram-telegramdesktop-beta-icon', ''),
('telerik-fiddler-classic', 'Progress Telerik Fiddler Classic', 'Fiddler is a Web Debugging Proxy which logs all HTTP(S) traffic between your computer and the Internet.
Fiddler allows you to inspect all HTTP(S) traffic, set breakpoints, and "fiddle" with incoming or outgoing data. Fiddler includes a powerful event-based scripting subsystem, and can be extended using any .NET language.
Fiddler is freeware and can debug traffic from virtually any application, including Internet Explorer, Mozilla Firefox, Opera, and thousands more.', 'Utilities', 'telerik-fiddler-classic-icon', ''),
('telerik-fiddler-everywhere', 'Fiddler Everywhere', 'Fiddler Everywhere is a secure and modern web debugging proxy for macOS, Windows, and Linux.', 'Utilities', 'telerik-fiddler-everywhere-icon', ''),
('telerik-fiddler-everywhere-insiders', 'Fiddler Everywhere Insiders', 'Fiddler Everywhere is a secure and modern web debugging proxy for macOS, Windows, and Linux.', 'Development', 'telerik-fiddler-everywhere-insiders-icon', ''),
('tenable-nessus', 'Tenable Nessus', 'Nessus is a Vulnerability Scanner developed by Tenable', 'Development', 'tenable-nessus-icon', ''),
('tencent-arthub', 'ArtHub', 'ArtHub Digital Asset Management System is a cloud-based solution for game art production developed by Tencent CROS to meet the needs of content production teams and collaborative outsourcing teams within the company. It aims to connect all aspects, processes and team members of art production, helping content creation teams to produce high-standard digital assets in a more efficient way.', 'Games', 'tencent-arthub-icon', ''),
('tencent-cosbrowser', 'cosbrowser', 'COSBrowser is a visual interface tool launched by Tencent Cloud to make it easier and simpler for you to view, transfer, manage, and interact with COS resources.', 'Utilities', 'tencent-cosbrowser-icon', ''),
('tencent-coscli', 'COSCLI', 'COS provides the command-line client COSCLI to allow you to upload, download, delete, and perform other operations on COS objects by using simple commands.', 'Development', 'tencent-coscli-icon', ''),
('tencent-foxmail', 'Foxmail', 'Simple, yet not common. Efficient, yet effortless. Enjoy easier communication, yet keep all the hassles from work at bay.', 'Social', 'tencent-foxmail-icon', ''),
('tencent-start', 'START', 'Tencent START is a gaming platform that enables you to play your favorite video games instantly on screens you already own without downloading them.', 'Games', 'tencent-start-icon', ''),
('tencent-tim', 'TIM', 'TIM is an efficient office software from Tencent that focuses on work, collaboration and communication with powerful office features such as Tencent Docs (Word/Excel), cloud file storage, email and voice conferencing. It can make team collaboration more convenient with its refreshing interface and easy operation, helping you improve your work efficiency immediately.', 'Office', 'tencent-tim-icon', ''),
('tencent-tencentmeeting', 'Tencent Meeting', 'Backed by Tencent''s 21 years of experience in audiovisual communications and Tencent Cloud''s global network deployment, Tencent Meeting provides smooth, secure, and reliable cloud-based HD conferencing services that enable you to start or join meetings with ease anytime, anywhere. It features online document collaboration, join via WeChat Mini Programs, meeting management and control, screen sharing and many more. With Tencent Meeting, mobile working and cross-company meetings are no longer a problem!', 'Development', 'tencent-tencentmeeting-icon', ''),
('tencent-tencentmeetingrooms', 'TencentMeetingRooms', 'Tencent Meeting Rooms is a software system built specifically for meeting rooms that provides an integrated meeting experience with audio/video conferencing, wireless screen casting and interactive whiteboards, publishes audio/video authentication standards, and selects branded hardware consoles to provide a modern meeting room solution for enterprises together.', 'Development', 'tencent-tencentmeetingrooms-icon', ''),
('tencent-transmart', 'TranSmart', 'Tencent Interactive Translation TranSmart is an AI-assisted translation product released by Tencent AI Lab, which can meet users'' needs for rapid translation and improve the efficiency and quality of human translation with AI-assisted translation. Using the team''s self-developed human-machine interactive machine translation technology, combined with a number of cutting-edge technologies such as neural network machine translation, statistical machine translation, input method, semantic understanding and data mining, as well as billions of bilingual parallel data, TranSmart is an AI-assisted translation Internet product that can provide users with real-time intelligent translation assistance and help them complete translation tasks better and faster.', 'Development', 'tencent-transmart-icon', ''),
('tencent-voovmeeting', 'VooV Meeting', 'Backed by Tencent''s 21 years of experience in audiovisual communications, VooV Meeting provides one-stop cloud-based conferencing solutions. The high-definition and smooth audiovisual quality allows you to experience immersive conference collaboration anytime, anywhere.', 'Development', 'tencent-voovmeeting-icon', ''),
('tencent-wechat', 'WeChat', 'Connecting over a billion people around the world, WeChat is a free messaging and calling app available on iOS, Android, Windows, and MacOS. Enjoy group chats that support voice and video calls, photos, videos, and stickers.', 'Development', 'tencent-wechat-icon', ''),
('tencent-weiyun', 'WeiyunApp', 'Weiyun is an intelligent cloud service by Tencent where you can sync files, send photos and transfer data between your phone and computer conveniently.', 'Design', 'tencent-weiyun-icon', ''),
('tencent-wemeetoutlookplugin', 'Tencent Meeting Outlook Plugin', 'tencent meeting outlook plugin', 'Office', 'tencent-wemeetoutlookplugin-icon', 'Thunderbird / Evolution'),
('tenpi-musicplayer', 'Music Player', 'A music player with real-time pitch shifting, reversing, and time stretching', 'Audio', 'tenpi-musicplayer-icon', ''),
('tenpi-photoviewer', 'Photo Viewer', 'An image/GIF viewer that can apply various resizing and color effects.', 'Design', 'tenpi-photoviewer-icon', ''),
('tenpi-videoplayer', 'Video Player', 'A video player with reversing and time stretching effects', 'Development', 'tenpi-videoplayer-icon', ''),
('tenpi-waifu2xgui', 'Waifu2x GUI', 'A GUI app that upscales anime-styled images with waifu2x', 'Development', 'tenpi-waifu2xgui-icon', ''),
('teratermproject-teraterm', 'Tera Term', 'open-source, free, software terminal emulator', 'Utilities', 'teratermproject-teraterm-icon', ''),
('teraskull-pydebloatx', 'PyDebloatX', 'A simple way to uninstall the default Windows 10 apps.', 'Utilities', 'teraskull-pydebloatx-icon', ''),
('terminals-terminals', 'Terminals', 'Multi tab terminal services/remote desktop client.', 'Utilities', 'terminals-terminals-icon', ''),
('termius-termius', 'Termius', 'Termius is the SSH client that works on Desktop and Mobile', 'Utilities', 'termius-termius-icon', ''),
('terraform-docs-terraform-docs', 'terraform-docs', 'A utility to generate documentation from Terraform modules in various output formats.', 'Office', 'terraform-docs-terraform-docs-icon', ''),
('terraformlinters-tflint', 'TFLint', 'A Pluggable Terraform Linter', 'Utilities', 'terraformlinters-tflint-icon', ''),
('terrastruct-d2', 'D2', 'A modern diagram scripting language that turns text to diagrams.', 'Utilities', 'terrastruct-d2-icon', ''),
('tetrate-func-e', 'func-e', 'func-e (pronounced funky) allows you to quickly see available versions of Envoy and try them out. This makes it easy to validate configuration you would use in production. Each time you end a run, a snapshot of runtime state is taken on your behalf. This makes knowledge sharing and troubleshooting easier, especially when upgrading. Try it out!', 'Utilities', 'tetrate-func-e-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxcasstudent', 'TI-Nspire CX CAS Student Software', 'Powerful computer software with a Computer Algebra System (CAS) that satisfies math and science curriculum needs from middle school through college.', 'Utilities', 'texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxcasstudent-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxpremiumteacher', 'TI-Nspire CX Premium Teacher Software', 'Present concepts, encourage discussion and assess understanding with software that turns a teacher’s PC or Mac into a virtual TI-Nspire™ CX II graphing calculator.', 'Utilities', 'texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxpremiumteacher-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxstudent', 'TI-Nspire CX Student Software', 'Powerful computer software that satisfies math and science curriculum needs from middle school through college.', 'Utilities', 'texasinstruments-ti-nspire-cxstudent-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-nspire-computerlink', 'TI-Nspire™ Computer Link', 'Share files between the TI-Nspire™ handheld and your computer with TI-Nspire™ Computer Link Software.', 'Utilities', 'texasinstruments-ti-nspire-computerlink-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-smartview-mathprint', 'TI-SmartView for MathPrint Calculators', 'Demonstrate and lead classroom exploration of math and science concepts with easy-to-use software that emulates the TI-30XS MultiView™, TI-30XB MultiView™ and TI-34 MultiView™ scientific calculators.', 'Design', 'texasinstruments-ti-smartview-mathprint-icon', '');

INSERT INTO apps (id, name, description, category, icon, linux_alternative) VALUES
('texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-83', 'TI-SmartView CE pour la famille TI-83', 'The TI-SmartView™ CE software allows you to display a TI graphing calculator for your entire classroom.', 'Design', 'texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-83-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-84plus', 'TI-SmartView CE for the TI-84 Plus Family', 'The TI-SmartView™ CE software allows you to display a TI graphing calculator for your entire classroom.', 'Design', 'texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-84plus-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-collegeplus', 'TI-SmartView™ TI-Collège™ Plus', 'The TI-SmartView™ software allows you to display a TI graphing calculator for your entire classroom.', 'Design', 'texasinstruments-ti-smartview-ti-collegeplus-icon', ''),
('texasinstruments-ticonnect', 'TI Connect™', 'TI Connect™ is computer software that allows for connectivity between a computer and graphing calculator.
Transfer data, update your Operating System (OS), download Calculator Software Applications (Apps), and more to your graphing calculator.', 'Utilities', 'texasinstruments-ticonnect-icon', ''),
('texmaker-texmaker', 'Texmaker', 'Free cross-platform LaTeX editor since 2003.', 'Design', 'texmaker-texmaker-icon', ''),
('texnomic-securedns-terminal', 'Texnomic SecureDNS Terminal', 'Secure, Modern, Fully-Featured Cross-Architecture & Cross-Platform DNS Server Using C# 8.0 & .NET Core 3.1', 'Utilities', 'texnomic-securedns-terminal-icon', ''),
('thaunknown-miru', 'Miru', 'A pure JS BitTorrent streaming environment, with a built-in list manager. Imagine qBit + Taiga + MPV, all in a single package, but streamed real-time. Completly ad free with no tracking/data collection. This app is meant to feel look, work and perform like a streaming website/app, while providing all the advantages of torrenting, like file downloads, higher download speeds, better video quality and quicker releases. Unlike qBit''s sequential, seeking into undownloaded data will prioritise downloading that data, instead of flat out closing MPV.', 'Development', 'thaunknown-miru-icon', ''),
('thaddeusmccleary-seatsmart', 'Seatsmart', 'a classroom participation tracking application', 'Design', 'thaddeusmccleary-seatsmart-icon', ''),
('thatonecalculator-discordrpcmaker', 'Discord RPC Maker', 'Cross-platform Discord Rich Presence Generator, WITH BUTTONS!', 'Utilities', 'thatonecalculator-discordrpcmaker-icon', ''),
('thedocumentfoundation-libreoffice', 'LibreOffice', 'LibreOffice is a free and powerful office suite, and a successor to OpenOffice.org (commonly known as OpenOffice). Its clean interface and feature-rich tools help you unleash your creativity and enhance your productivity.', 'Office', 'thedocumentfoundation-libreoffice-icon', ''),
