('universityofwaikato-weka', 'Weka', 'Weka is a collection of machine learning algorithms for solving real-world data mining problems. It is written in Java and runs on almost any platform. The algorithms can either be applied directly to a dataset or called from your own Java code.', 'Development', 'universityofwaikato-weka-icon', ''),
