('unlimitedbacon-stl-thumb', 'STL-Thumb', 'Stl-thumb is a fast lightweight thumbnail generator for STL files. It can show previews for STL files in your file manager on Linux and Windows. It is written in Rust and uses OpenGL.', 'Utilities', 'unlimitedbacon-stl-thumb-icon', ''),
