('urbackup-urbackup-client', 'UrBackup', 'UrBackup is an easy to setup Open Source client/server backup system, that through a combination of image and file backups accomplishes both data safety and a fast restoration time.', 'Design', 'urbackup-urbackup-client-icon', ''),
