('ventismedia-mediamonkey', 'MediaMonkey', 'Manage small to large collections of audio files, videos and playlists (100,000+), whether on a hard drive, network, or CDs. Rip CDs, download podcasts, lookup artwork and other missing information online, tag almost any audio or video format, and automatically rename/re-organize files on your hard drive.', 'Development', 'ventismedia-mediamonkey-icon', ''),
('vercel-hyper', 'Hyper', 'A terminal built on web technologies', 'Utilities', 'vercel-hyper-icon', ''),
('vertexshare-webpconverter', 'Webp Converter', 'Convert hundreds of WebP images to JPG/JPEG/PNG/GIF, or from any other image formats to WebP on your Win/Mac computer!', 'Design', 'vertexshare-webpconverter-icon', ''),
('veyonsolutions-veyon', 'Veyon', 'Veyon is a free and open source software for monitoring and controlling computers across multiple platforms. Veyon supports you in teaching in digital learning environments, performing virtual trainings or giving remote support.', 'Development', 'veyonsolutions-veyon-icon', ''),
('vigem-hidhide', 'HidHide', 'Gaming input peripherals device firewall for Windows.', 'Games', 'vigem-hidhide-icon', ''),
('vigem-vigembus', 'ViGEm Bus Driver', 'Windows kernel-mode driver emulating well-known USB game controllers.', 'Games', 'vigem-vigembus-icon', ''),
('viber-viber', 'Viber', 'Viber is a mobile application that lets you make free phone calls and send text messages to anyone who also has the application installed. You can call or text any Viber user, anywhere in the world, for free.', 'Social', 'viber-viber-icon', ''),
('videolan-vlc', 'VLC media player', 'VLC is a free and open source cross-platform multimedia player and framework that plays most multimedia files as well as DVDs, Audio CDs, VCDs, and various streaming protocols.

Simple, fast and powerful
✓ Plays everything - Files, Discs, Webcams, Devices and Streams.
✓ Pays most codecs with no codec packs needed - MPEG-2, MPEG-4, H.264, MKV, WebM, WMV, MP3...
✓ Runs on all platforms - Windows, Linux, Mac OS X, Unix, iOS, Android ...
✓ Completely Free - no spyware, no ads and no user tracking.', 'Development', 'videolan-vlc-icon', ''),
('videolan-x264', 'x264', 'x264 is a free software library and application for encoding video streams into the H.264/MPEG-4 AVC compression format.', 'Development', 'videolan-x264-icon', ''),
('viewsonic-myviewboard-display', 'myViewBoard Display', 'myViewBoard Display for Windows turns any device into a wireless display that can be shared to with just a code and password.', 'Development', 'viewsonic-myviewboard-display-icon', ''),
('viewsonic-myviewboard-whiteboard', 'myViewBoard Whiteboard', 'myViewBoard Whiteboard for Windows is a digital whiteboard designed to run on the Windows operating system. Whiteboard features work best on large touchscreen displays.', 'Development', 'viewsonic-myviewboard-whiteboard-icon', ''),
('vinaysajip-pythonlauncher', 'Python Launcher', 'The launcher allows Python scripts (.py and .pyw files) on Windows to specify the version of Python which should be used, allowing simultaneous use of Python 2 and 3.', 'Games', 'vinaysajip-pythonlauncher-icon', ''),
('vincentl-harmony', 'Harmony', 'Sleek music player for Spotify, SoundCloud, Google Play Music and your local files', 'Audio', 'vincentl-harmony-icon', ''),
('vipre-ipvtest', 'IPVTest', 'To test Git HUB', 'Development', 'vipre-ipvtest-icon', ''),
('virtualdesktop-streamer', 'Virtual Desktop Streamer', 'Watch movies, browse the web or play games on a giant virtual screen.', 'Games', 'virtualdesktop-streamer-icon', ''),
('virtualgl-turbovnc', 'TurboVNC', 'TurboVNC is a high-performance, enterprise-quality version of VNC based on TightVNC, TigerVNC, and X.org.
It contains a variant of Tight encoding that is tuned for maximum performance and compression with 3D applications (VirtualGL), video, and other image-intensive workloads.
TurboVNC, in combination with VirtualGL, provides a complete solution for remotely displaying 3D applications with interactive performance.
TurboVNC''s high-speed encoding methods have been adopted by TigerVNC and libvncserver, and TurboVNC is also compatible with any other TightVNC derivative.', 'Development', 'virtualgl-turbovnc-icon', ''),
('virtualgl-virtualgl', 'VirtualGL-Utils', 'VirtualGL redirects 3D commands from a Unix/Linux OpenGL application onto a server-side GPU and converts the rendered 3D images into a video stream with which remote clients can interact to view and control the 3D application in real time.', 'Development', 'virtualgl-virtualgl-icon', ''),
('virtualhere-usbclient', 'VirtualHere USB Client', 'The VirtualHere USB Client runs on Windows, MacOS, Linux and Android. The client was created to be intuitive and extremely easy to use.
