('wondershare-anireel', 'Wondershare Anireel', 'Anireel is an easy animated explainer video editor with rich ready-to-use assets, effortlessly make animated videos for marketing, knowledge sharing, elearning.', 'Development', 'wondershare-anireel-icon', ''),
('wondershare-creativecenter', 'Wondershare Creative Center', 'Creative Center gives you simple, convenient, and useful tools to help you create attractive videos in minutes and save them on the cloud. Share your ideas in our built-in creative community.', 'Development', 'wondershare-creativecenter-icon', ''),
('wondershare-cropro', 'Wondershare Cropro', 'Cropro lets you quickly capture any screen, make visual how-to guides, give better feedback and make your communication more productive.', 'Development', 'wondershare-cropro-icon', ''),
('wondershare-dvdcreator', 'Wondershare DVD Creator', 'Wondershare DVD Creator is a powerful and easy-to-use DVD and Blu-ray Disc burner app to burn photos and videos to DVD/Blu-ray disc with built-in editor and gorgeous free DVD menu templates so that you make personalized DVD by your needs.', 'Development', 'wondershare-dvdcreator-icon', ''),
('wondershare-democreator', 'Wondershare DemoCreator', 'Wondershare DemoCreator is a professional presentation video creation tool that integrates recording and editing to help you create videos more efficiently. Using DemoCreator, you can not only experience high-definition screen recording, webcam capture, microphone voice-over recording, screen drawing tool, spotlight, and other practical recording functions. You can also use the built-in video templates, transition effects, green screen chroma key, Pan&Zoom, stickers, and other hundreds of editing tools and presentation video templates to help you create videos with ease.
DemoCreator has made special optimizations for video creation such as presentations, online training, and game recording. It supports the audio and video sub-track editing of the recorded files according to the input source. It uses cursor effects, audio fade-in and fade-out, and other post-production tools to accurately modify the video material so that you can make better use of the video material. During game recording, unique adaptations and optimizations have been made for various popular games to stabilize the image capture and enhance the game recording experience.', 'Games', 'wondershare-democreator-icon', ''),
('wondershare-famisafe', 'Wondershare FamiSafe', 'FamiSafe lets parents control screen time, track real-time location and detect inappropriate content on kids'' devices.', 'Utilities', 'wondershare-famisafe-icon', ''),
('wondershare-filmii', 'Wondershare Filmii', 'Wondershare Filmii is a video editor with tons of creative AI-powered templates that instantly transform your clips into shareworthy videos! There’s a style for every mood that can be personalized however you like. Making videos is now fun, fast, and carefree.', 'Development', 'wondershare-filmii-icon', ''),
('wondershare-filmora', 'Wondershare Filmora 12', 'Filmora is an intuitive video editor for every skill level. Filmora makes it easy for anyone to be creative. Jump into an editing experience where advanced features are simple and fun. We got rid of repetitive tasks so you can devote your energy to your imagination. Get inspired by Filmora, an editor designed for creators like you.', 'Development', 'wondershare-filmora-icon', ''),
('wondershare-filmora-pro', 'Wondershare FilmoraPro', 'A powerful video editor with professional effects and keyframing.', 'Development', 'wondershare-filmora-pro-icon', ''),
('wondershare-fotophire-focus', 'Fotophire Photo Focus', 'Wondershare Fotophire Photo Focus helps you fix blurry photos and refocus the way you want.', 'Design', 'wondershare-fotophire-focus-icon', ''),
('wondershare-fotophire-maximizer', 'Fotophire Photo Maximizer', 'Photo Maximizer can enlarge your photo to 1000% while reconstructing the sharpness to maintain high resolution.', 'Design', 'wondershare-fotophire-maximizer-icon', ''),
('wondershare-fotophire-slideshowmaker', 'Wondershare Fotophire Slideshow Maker', 'Wondershare Fotophire Slideshow Maker helps you to make slideshows with photos and videos in 3 simple steps. More than 180 templates are offered to make your slideshow unique and outstanding.', 'Development', 'wondershare-fotophire-slideshowmaker-icon', ''),
