('wondershare-hipdf', 'Wondershare HiPDF', 'Wondershare HiPDF is an all-in-one online PDF editor from which you can get powerful features to edit, review, protect, sign and convert PDFs.', 'Design', 'wondershare-hipdf-icon', ''),
