('wondershare-mockitt-cn', 'mockingbot-studio', 'MODAO, an integrated online collaboration platform for product design, is an essential tool for designers, product managers and development teams. It integrates prototyping, online version of Sketch designer tools, flowcharts and mind maps, supports real-time collaboration and management of team projects, features financial-level data security, and supports private deployment.', 'Development', 'wondershare-mockitt-cn-icon', ''),
('wondershare-pdfconverter-pro', 'Wondershare PDF Converter Pro', 'Convert PDFs into secure file formats, like image, Microsoft Office, etc. with high-quality and minimum effort.', 'Design', 'wondershare-pdfconverter-pro-icon', ''),
('wondershare-pdfpasswordremover', 'Wondershare PDF Password Remover', 'Wondershare PDF Password Remover is a small and easy-to-use PDF cracker to help you remove PDF password and restrictions in seconds.', 'Office', 'wondershare-pdfpasswordremover-icon', 'LibreOffice Writer / ONLYOFFICE'),
