('xk72-charles', 'Charles', 'Charles is an HTTP proxy / HTTP monitor / Reverse Proxy that enables a developer to view all of the HTTP and SSL / HTTPS traffic between their machine and the Internet. This includes requests, responses and the HTTP headers (which contain the cookies and caching information).', 'Development', 'xk72-charles-icon', ''),
('xmoto-xmoto', 'xmoto', 'X-Moto is a challenging 2D motocross platform game, where physics play an all important role in the gameplay. You need to control your bike to its limit, if you want to have a chance finishing the more difficult of the challenges.', 'Games', 'xmoto-xmoto-icon', ''),
