('xanthus58-valorantrandomizer', 'Valorant Randomizer', 'A randomizer for Valorant; it has will automaticly select an agent; weapons and shields.', 'Utilities', 'xanthus58-valorantrandomizer-icon', ''),
('xanthus58-vanillarenewed', 'VanillaRenewed', 'Vanilla Renewed is a Res pack for Minecraft that intends to optimize, improve quality of life, and fix the game in various ways. Optifine is required for the intended experience.', 'Games', 'xanthus58-vanillarenewed-icon', ''),
('xavierroche-httrack', 'WinHTTrack Website Copier', 'HTTrack allows you to download a World Wide Web site from the Internet to a local directory, building recursively all directories, getting HTML, images, and other files from the server to your computer. HTTrack arranges the original site''s relative link-structure. Simply open a page of the "mirrored" website in your browser, and you can browse the site from link to link, as if you were viewing it online.', 'Development', 'xavierroche-httrack-icon', ''),
('xcas-xcas', 'Xcas', 'Xcas is a Giac interface, which allows computer algebra, graphical representations in the plane or space, dynamic geometry (in the plane or in space), spreadsheet, statistics and programming.
