('xmind-xmind-8', 'XMind 8', 'XMind, a full-featured mind mapping and brainstorming tool, designed to generate ideas, inspire creativity, brings efficiency both in work and life. Millions and millions of people love it.', 'Development', 'xmind-xmind-8-icon', ''),
