('xnsoft-xnview-classic', 'XnView', 'XnView is an efficient image viewer, browser and converter for Windows. This software is really simple to use and totally free for personal use. It supports more than 500 image formats!', 'Design', 'xnsoft-xnview-classic-icon', ''),
