('yandex-disk', 'Yandex Disk', 'Yandex Disk is a Yandex 360 service. Your own space to manage day-to-day tasks - from storing personal memories to writing business emails.', 'Utilities', 'yandex-disk-icon', ''),
('yandex-puntoswitcher', 'Punto Switcher', 'Punto Switcher is a program that automatically switches keyboard layouts. She knows that "ghbdtn" is "hello," and "pshschw shchktshtp" is "good morning." And you know that with Punto Switcher your layout is always correct.', 'Utilities', 'yandex-puntoswitcher-icon', ''),
('yarn-yarn', 'Yarn', 'Yarn is a package manager that doubles down as project manager. Whether you work on one-shot projects or large monorepos, as a hobbyist or an enterprise user, we''ve got you covered.', 'Utilities', 'yarn-yarn-icon', ''),
